            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "They think that recruitment is a joke; they will hire and fire as they wish after wasting time for around 15–18 days since the interview. They hold me up by saying I'm selected for PRT; then, of course, I'll be mentally prepared to join here and not go for other interviews. Even though they confirmed the joining date, due to the disunity of the management and the owner, they decided not to let the new teachers join because the strength of the students didn't meet their expectations. So they decided to hire and fire unofficially and unethically. I'm not the only one; there are other people too who faced the same challenges. The fake commitment by the seniors in this school is really unexpected.",
