          "reviewBody": "I am 2015 batch student, today after becoming an advocate I miss the time when I was in a school. School is great but faculty is partially supported only few students. The only thing I hate about the school is that they gaved us a punishment of our seniors doing by not to take us in a ground in physical education period and also by not conducting a farewell for us, they maybe didn't understand the importance of last goodbye that's why they did this to us and for that I always hate our management.",
